## Design Overview

CovertEDA is a unified FPGA development frontend wrapping vendor CLIs (Lattice Diamond/Radiant, Intel Quartus, AMD Vivado, Achronix ACE) and open-source toolchains (Yosys/nextpnr) behind a single interface.

